Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:51.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊哈，洋葱头，无处可躲了吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is it, Onion. Nowhere to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:53.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在放-放下零食和-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now just -- just drop the bag and --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:55.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...洋葱头？\N{\fnArial\fs48}uh...Onion?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:01:57.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:01:59.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:04.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...这就有点诡异了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...That's really weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:11.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，所以...我一直清楚洋葱头有点怪，但...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um, so...I always knew Onion was weird, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:13.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我感觉他对你有点那啥？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think he's obsessed with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.63,0:02:15.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你觉得呢，紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you think, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.64,0:02:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谁在那里？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Who's in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:19.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，我不知道你如何绕过油布的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now, I don't know how you got past that tarp,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这可是私人领地\N{\fnArial\fs48}but this is private property.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}维达利亚？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Vidalia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.20,0:02:24.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst?!
