Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.48,0:02:29.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}天，你变了好多\N{\fnArial\fs48}Man, you've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:31.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看起来糟透了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You look terrible!
