Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.78,0:02:41.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，我们都和你爸有交往，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, we both kind of hung around your dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:43.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但维达利亚比你爸更酷，\N{\fnArial\fs48}but Vidalia's cooler than your dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:45.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以我们便开始单独交往了\N{\fnArial\fs48}so we started hanging out without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.78,0:02:48.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是史蒂文吧？看看\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that Steven? Look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:49.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}长得和格雷格一模一样\N{\fnArial\fs48}He looks just like Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:52.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没什么，没什么，他原来可帅了\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's good. That's good. He used to be super hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，所以你们原来在一起时画的这些？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, so did you paint these when you used to hang out?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是啊，应该说是一部分，不过有些是新画的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, some of them. Some are new, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶曾是我最喜欢的模特\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst was my favorite model.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:06.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你仍然可以变成任何物体吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can you still turn into anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然，不过正经的不行\N{\fnArial\fs48}Anything but respectable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.66,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}此处紫晶的造型致敬毕加索的超现实立体派肖像画
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:13.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，天哪，我们之前可惹过各种麻烦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, man, we used to get into all sorts of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:15.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来告诉我，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now tell me, Steven,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们算不算叛逆先锋？\N{\fnArial\fs48}aren't we just the spitting image of mischief?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:20.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}勉强把\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么穿拖鞋了\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're wearing slippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你可猜不到我用这双鞋干过什么\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't know what I've done in these shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}很高兴再次见到你\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's great to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:30.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起好久没联系了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry it's been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我猜我们都很忙吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}I guess we've both been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，对啊，我知道-小孩嘛\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, yeah. I get it -- kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}孩子怎么了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What about kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:37.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，这就有个\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, here's one now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:42.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是洋葱头的妈妈？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're Onion's mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.14,0:03:43.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他就是我的小捣蛋鬼\N{\fnArial\fs48}He's my little troublemaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:48.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且，史蒂文，他很喜欢谈论你\N{\fnArial\fs48}And, Steven, he loves talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，那是个好主意！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, that's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，紫晶，洋葱头想知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, Amethyst, Onion wants to know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们愿不愿离留下吃晚餐\N{\fnArial\fs48}if you'd like to stay for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:03:58.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然啦，\N{\fnArial\fs48}We'd love to,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对吧，史蒂文？洋葱头就像，你的好朋友\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right, Steven? Onion's, like, your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:05.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在，该告诉我你穿着拖鞋做过什么了吧，妹子？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now, tell me what you did in those shoes, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:08.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可没法再多塞一口\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mm, I can't eat another bite of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:10.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那种不可言状的玩意了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whatever that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，那只是一道\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, it's just a little dish
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我起名为奶油炒面条的菜\N{\fnArial\fs48}I like to call noodles and butter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我简直不敢相信过了这么久\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe how long it's been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.38,0:04:18.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是说，看看他\N{\fnArial\fs48}I mean, check this guy out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我之前可是比他高的\N{\fnArial\fs48}I used to be bigger than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.39,0:04:24.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你之后有臭子马蒂的消息吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Do you ever hear from old farty Marty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:24.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:29.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我可不知道那个笨蛋在哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know where that fool is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也不在乎\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't care, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}之后一直是我和黄鳍在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's just been me and Yellowtail for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}黄鳍？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yellowtail?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:38.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}没错，我们直接来了电\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, things just kind of happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}之后，我就和渔民在一起了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Next thing you know, I'm living with a fisherman.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.82,0:04:44.34,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}你该看看你的表情\N{\fnArial\fs48}You should see your face right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，酸奶油\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, Sour Cream.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.64,0:04:48.60,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HD897C1&}我怎么猜得到？\N{\fnArial\fs48}I just didn't expect any of this.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.62,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}好吧，事情现在就是这样\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, that's just how it is now.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.59,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HD897C1&}那么现在老鱼鳍在哪？\N{\fnArial\fs48}So where's old fish tail at?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:52.59,0:04:54.22,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}呃，是“黄鳍”\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, it's Yellowtail.
