Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.60,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}他大部分时间在海上\N{\fnArial\fs48}He spends a lot of time out at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:57.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，那是我\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, it's me.
