Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.22,0:05:02.56,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}码头的那种味道\N{\fnArial\fs48}about the smell at the docks.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.64,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}那里原来可恶心了\N{\fnArial\fs48}It used to be so gross over there.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.64,0:05:06.90,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}现在那里\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now there are all these fancy boats hanging around.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.90,0:05:09.52,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}还记得我们曾偷偷进入市长的船然后乱搞一气吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Remember when we snuck on to the mayor's boat and trashed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么你这么讨厌食物？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why do you hate food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:12.27,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对啊，我还记得\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:13.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你呢，紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What about you, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.98,0:05:14.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你一晚上还没说过你的故事呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}You haven't said a word about yourself all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:19.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}其实，这是因为我的生活太无聊了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, that's because my life is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，宝石人们怎么样？\N{\fnArial\fs48}All right, how are the gems?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不知道，她们也很无聊\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't know. They're boring, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.12,0:05:26.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，谢谢你们的晚安，该走了，不是吗，紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, thanks for dinner. Time to go, right, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}急什么集？我们又没事做\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's the hurry? We got nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:32.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}另，紫晶/维达利亚派对从不停止\N{\fnArial\fs48}'Sides, an amethyst/vidalia party don't end
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}除非太阳出来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}till the sun come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:34.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}妈-妈\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ma-ma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:35.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}妈妈妈妈-麻麻-嘛-码-码-嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:39.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，那是个好主意！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, that's a great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:42.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，洋葱头想带你看看屋子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, Onion wants to show you around the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么样？让洋葱头带你看看？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What do you say? Can Onion tote you around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:52.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃..发..发生了什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh... W-what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:55.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，每当酸奶油开始打碟，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, whenever Sour Cream starts deejaying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:57.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就会用光整栋房的电力\N{\fnArial\fs48}it uses all the electricity in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:58.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还好黄鳍不在家-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Good thing Yellowtail's not here --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这能逼疯他的\N{\fnArial\fs48}it drives him nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}伙计，你的房子嗨上天了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Dude, your house is jacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.04,0:06:05.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能怎么办？孩子们要表现自我\N{\fnArial\fs48}What can you do? Kids got to express themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:09.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你也是，洋葱头\N{\fnArial\fs48}You too, Onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.36,0:06:10.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}相当有表现力\N{\fnArial\fs48}Very expressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}看来他准备好了，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Looks like he's ready for you, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...挺酷的购物车\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh... Cool shopping cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.62,0:06:24.28,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}洋葱头床头的海报致敬摇滚乐队The Door
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}为什么你不在蹦床上跳呢？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why don't you just jump up and down on that trampoline?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:30.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我是说，就像，在那\N{\fnArial\fs48}I mean, it's, like, right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:32.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但这是你的房间...\N{\fnArial\fs48}But it's your room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:34.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}..那么随你便啦\N{\fnArial\fs48}...So do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:38.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你还有个小老鼠做室友！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have a little mousy roommate friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗷～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aww!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:39.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那是你的宠物？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is that your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:48.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，他一定住那里，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, that must be where he lives, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我帮你将他放回家\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me help you put him in his home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:53.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这对小宝宝来讲真是个大箱-\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is a pretty large container for a little baby --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}蛇！\N{\fnArial\fs48}snake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N洋葱头，你想让我{\fnArial\fs48}Onion, you want me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:00.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}用我们的小伙伴喂蛇吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}to feed our little friend to this snake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:04.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对不起，但我们都得吃饭的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sorry, but we all got to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:09.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我...\N{\fnArial\fs48}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}做不到！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:14.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃！赶紧把他从我手里拿走吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh! Just take him from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:15.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我就在这里\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I'll be over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.98,0:07:19.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:22.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你不会再给我看更多的奇怪宠物了，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You don't have any more weird pets to show me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你要放电影？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You gonna put on a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:28.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那真不错-一点也不怪异\N{\fnArial\fs48}That'd be nice -- and not creepy at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}医院布景不错嘛\N{\fnArial\fs48}Cool hospital setting.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.26,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}好的，我准备好了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，那是你妈妈\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, that's your mom.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.38,0:07:34.16,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}我准备好了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她准备好做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's she getting ready for?
