Dialogue: 100,0:07:36.55,0:07:38.66,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}哦-黄鳍-我觉得...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, Yellowtail, I think...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:38.95,0:07:40.78,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}哦-他要出来了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, it's happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，等下！发生了什么？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh, wait! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.88,0:07:43.96,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}他来了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Here he comes!
Dialogue: 500,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.80,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\fn隶书\fs128\frz13.72\pos(974,324)\c&H6143B1&\bord0\shad0}生日快乐，洋葱头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.28,0:07:49.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是你出生的视频吗？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is this you being born?!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:48.48,0:07:51.10,Background Dialogue,Vidalia,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HB9F1FA&}哦，我坚持不下去了-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, I am never doing this --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.36,0:07:53.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我没法再承受了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't take much more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.41,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}这个很明显了，《肖申克的救赎》里的越狱隧道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.47,0:07:57.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哪里？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.60,0:08:02.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，我得走了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:04.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不能再继续了，得回家了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can't do this anymore. Need to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:07.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，对不起，但是时候-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, I'm sorry, but it's time to --
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.52,0:08:06.78,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HD897C1&}所有事都一团糟\N{\fnArial\fs48}Everything is a mess,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.92,0:08:11.24,Background Dialogue,Amethyst,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64\pos(960,120)\c&HD897C1&}即使是石榴，就像，我从没见过石榴这么生气过\N{\fnArial\fs48}even Garnet, like, I've never seen Garnet this upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.68,0:08:14.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}家里感觉非常遭，我感觉非常压抑\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's awful at home. I feel trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:17.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那真是太夸张了，不过我知道你的意思\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's crazy. I know what you mean, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:17.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}真的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，我们一家并不总是相处的非常愉快\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, we don't always get along in this family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}黄鳍和酸奶油总是相互掐架\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yellowtail and Sour Cream are always at each other's throats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:25.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这让我非常苦恼\N{\fnArial\fs48}It makes me nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:27.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}实际上，每当我烦恼时，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Actually, when I get like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:28.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我总想到你\N{\fnArial\fs48}I think about you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还有你毫不在乎的态度\N{\fnArial\fs48}and how you could always just roll with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:31.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:33.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不！就是你\N{\fnArial\fs48}No! That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你当初是那么...酷\N{\fnArial\fs48}You were so...Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我就像...一个跟着你的蠢海绵\N{\fnArial\fs48}I was just like...A dumb sponge following you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但你，遇事沉着，心无畏惧\N{\fnArial\fs48}But you were down for anything, not afraid of anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:44.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你知道我有多想变成你吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You know how much I wanted to be like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，我现在仍然这么认为\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh. I still think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:50.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}说实话，这也是为什么我再次开始画你的画像\N{\fnArial\fs48}To be honest, that's why I started painting you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:53.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我深受你的激励，紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm -- I'm inspired by you, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，看来我得再泡一杯茶了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, looks like I'm gonna need more tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.90,0:08:57.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你想吃了茶包吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You want to eat this bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然啊，这可是最爱\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, my favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.12,0:09:00.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好的，我很快就回来\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.34,0:09:03.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}还好孩子们一直有事情做\N{\fnArial\fs48}Good thing the kids are keeping themselves busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:09.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，洋葱头，继续吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, Onion, let's do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:12.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}无论你准备了多么怪异或恐怖的东西，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whatever weird or horrible thing you have planned for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.81,0:09:13.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我都能接住\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，慢点\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:27.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，天哪，这可不会有什么好结果\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, boy. This is gonna be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:27.34,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}此处画面的移动方式与周边游戏Attack the Light相同
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:31.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，呃，洋葱头，你在哪？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, uh, Onion, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是什么房间？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's this room?
Dialogue: 600,0:09:33.08,0:09:34.42,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}洋葱头的秘密房间与位置是皮克斯总部内部酒吧的再现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.08,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}此处洋葱头的画像致敬《2001太空漫游》中的星孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这里有什么？可怕的东西吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's in there? Something horrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:47.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}洋葱头！箱子里全是侠盗玩偶！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Onion! It's full of guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.36,0:09:48.24,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}红色的忍者侠盗致敬洛克人2中的Quickman
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.58,0:09:48.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我从没见过红色的忍者侠盗啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}I've never seen this red variant of ninja guy before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你还有女侠？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You have gals, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}安全帽女侠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hard hat gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}三角女侠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Triangle gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.50,0:09:56.40,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}粉色三角为同性恋同性恋斗争的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:57.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}橘子女侠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Orange gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:58.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}凯伦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Karen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:09:59.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}凯伦...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Karen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.82,Hint,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,50)}看起来像不像Rebecca Sugar（糖姐）？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是怎么收集到-不，别告诉我\N{\fnArial\fs48}How'd you get a hold of -- no, don't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:03.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:05.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不可能吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这是探险女侠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's explorer gal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她看起来可酷了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}She's so cool-looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.82,0:10:13.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢你让我看看她-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thanks for showing her to me --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:15.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-你应该收回你的探险女侠\N{\fnArial\fs48}you -- you should take your explorer gal back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是要送给我吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are you giving this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我简直不敢相信！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:24.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}太感谢你了，洋葱头！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thank you so much, Onion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗷，天哪！你还有什么侠盗和女侠？！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aw, man! What other gals and guys you got?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.90,0:10:29.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哈，太酷了-隐身侠盗\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ha, cool -- invisible guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们可以走啦\N{\fnArial\fs48}And stay out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.24,0:10:36.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，谢谢你们的晚餐-和倾听\N{\fnArial\fs48}Um, thanks for dinner -- and for listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然，也谢谢你们闯进我家\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, thanks for breaking into my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:40.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}同时不要担心那件事\N{\fnArial\fs48}And don't worry about that other stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.80,0:10:41.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那迟早会过去的\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's gonna blow over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你是块石头\N{\fnArial\fs48}You're a rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:44.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's what you are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:46.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，差不多吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么，不论你是什么，一定不要见外啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, whatever you are, don't be a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:53.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然，我随时可以来，只要你需要-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, I can stop by anytime if you need,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.52,0:10:54.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}灵感\N{\fnArial\fs48}inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.64,0:10:56.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}或者如果你需要，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Or if you want,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.94,0:10:59.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你也可以偶尔来神庙看看\N{\fnArial\fs48}you could come over to the temple sometime, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你也可以带上洋葱头来和史蒂文玩\N{\fnArial\fs48}You could even bring Onion for Steven to hang with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，当然，这听起来不错\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, well, that sounds great to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:05.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你呢，史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What about you, Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:07.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你准备好和他再来一局吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You ready for another round with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.20,0:11:14.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当然啦，改天见\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah, we'll see.
